data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News BNB Chain posted on the X platform that it hopes to clarify the following points about BNB Chain's position on cooperation and project representation: 
1. Any rumors of cooperation with a project party that have not been officially confirmed through official channels are false information; 
2. BNB Chain is open to all projects, developers, entrepreneurs, and even competitors. However, participating in events or conferences does not mean recognition or support for any specific project; 
3. Users and community members are strongly advised to verify information and rely on official communication channels for accurate updates; 
4. It has been found that pictures of important BNB community builders have been abused. Please note that such photos do not constitute recognition or approval of any third-party projects.
